flowchart LR
    A[Start] --> B{Dependencies OK?}

    B -->|No| C[Exit]
    B -->|Yes| D{Prompt Exists?}

    D -->|No| C
    D -->|Yes| E{Git Clean?}

    E -->|No| C
    E -->|Yes| F[Checkout Main]

    F --> G[Pull Latest]
    G --> H[Create Branch]

    H --> I[Run AI Loop]

    I --> J{.stuck exists?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Print Error]
    K --> L[Exit Failed]

    J -->|No| M{.complete exists?}

    M -->|Yes| N[Stop Loop]
    M -->|No| O{Iterations Left?}

    O -->|Yes| I
    O -->|No| N

    N --> P[Push Branch]

    P --> Q[Review Changes]

    Q --> R[Done]
